@pengys5 

> request: {"ac":"?","vm":{"?":"?"...}}
response: {"ii":"instance id"}

From your register service, you want agents to report `ApplicationCode` and `vm`, are you going to generate `instance id` by both `ac` and `vm`? Why do you need the `vm` info?

And if the instance-id includes applicationCode, does traceSegment still include applicationCode? If not, trace-receive-service needs translate instance-id of every traceSegment. By doing that, you need sync all instance-ids in the whole collector-cluster, are you sure about this?
